Acts 13-39 and by him <f>ⓞ</f>everyone who believes is freed <f>[3]</f> from everything <f>ⓟ</f>from which you could not be freed by the law of Moses.
Acts 13-40 Beware, therefore, lest what is said in the Prophets should come about:
